text: Illtal is a new commune in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. It was incorporated on 1 January 2016 by the combination of the former communes of Grentzingen, Henflingen and Oberdorf.Arrêté 17 December 2015 == References == Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 establishments in France
